import React from "react";

const HomeIcon = () => {
  return (
    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="43" height="43" viewBox="0 0 43 43">
      <g id="Groupe_9" data-name="Groupe 9" transform="translate(-94 -176)">
        <rect
          id="Rectangle_12"
          data-name="Rectangle 12"
          width="43"
          height="43"
          transform="translate(94 176)"
          fill="rgba(255,255,255,0)"
        />
        <g id="Icon_feather-home" data-name="Icon feather-home" transform="translate(107.778 188.92)">
          <path
            id="Tracé_2"
            data-name="Tracé 2"
            d="M4.5,9.006,12.222,3l7.722,6.006v9.437a1.716,1.716,0,0,1-1.716,1.716H6.216A1.716,1.716,0,0,1,4.5,18.443Z"
            transform="translate(-4.5 -3)"
            fill="none"
            stroke="#3d3939"
            strokeLinecap="round"
            strokeLinejoin="round"
            strokeWidth="1.2"
          />
          <path
            id="Tracé_3"
            data-name="Tracé 3"
            d="M13.5,26.58V18h5.148v8.58"
            transform="translate(-8.352 -9.42)"
            fill="none"
            stroke="#3d3939"
            strokeLinecap="round"
            strokeLinejoin="round"
            strokeWidth="1.2"
          />
        </g>
      </g>
    </svg>
  );
};

export default HomeIcon;
